  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the realistic forklift driver simulator in modern warehouses and distribution centers!</h2>Manage specialized equipment used in warehouses and become a professional in your field. The project is a complete training platform for forklift drivers. And the well-developed mechanics of the movement of specialized warehouse equipment allows you to experience the sensations of working in a warehouse without leaving your computer.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885640/extras/50faa7b3e2095872d7ed83cb60ea44b4.poster.avif?t=1773919331\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885640/extras/50faa7b3e2095872d7ed83cb60ea44b4.webm?t=1773919331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885640/extras/50faa7b3e2095872d7ed83cb60ea44b4.mp4?t=1773919331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >All tasks are performed with maximum accuracy to the processes used in warehouses</h2>There are already 3 types of tasks available in the game, which are present in most real warehouses:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Acceptance of pallets with goods<br></li><li>Placement of pallets with goods<br></li><li>Selection and shipment of pallets with goods</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the realistic forklift driver simulator in modern warehouses and distribution centers!</h2>Manage specialized equipment used in warehouses and become a professional in your field. The project is a complete training platform for forklift drivers. And the well-developed mechanics of the movement of specialized warehouse equipment allows you to experience the sensations of working in a warehouse without leaving your computer.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885640/extras/50faa7b3e2095872d7ed83cb60ea44b4.poster.avif?t=1773919331\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885640/extras/50faa7b3e2095872d7ed83cb60ea44b4.webm?t=1773919331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885640/extras/50faa7b3e2095872d7ed83cb60ea44b4.mp4?t=1773919331\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >All tasks are performed with maximum accuracy to the processes used in warehouses</h2>There are already 3 types of tasks available in the game, which are present in most real warehouses:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Acceptance of pallets with goods<br></li><li>Placement of pallets with goods<br></li><li>Selection and shipment of pallets with goods</li></ul>",
